WEBVTT


00:00:42.279 --> 00:00:43.119
Miss Lin

00:00:43.439 --> 00:00:44.880
From what I can tell, you have the looks

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:46.599
You don't need to rely on this to make money

00:00:46.919 --> 00:00:48.720
So why do you want to model for us?

00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:50.360
Money

00:00:50.720 --> 00:00:52.599
Can money buy the Rayli Star championship?

00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:54.360
That bastard

00:00:54.720 --> 00:00:56.880
He dumped me over some stupid title

00:00:57.159 --> 00:00:58.040
I want to see for myself

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:00.200
what magic the modeling world really has

00:01:00.919 --> 00:01:03.639
So you're a rich fool with a grudge, huh

00:01:04.599 --> 00:01:05.400
That's all?

00:01:05.639 --> 00:01:06.239
I get it

00:01:07.120 --> 00:01:08.680
With your assets, sweetheart,

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.160
forget online talent shows.

00:01:10.599 --> 00:01:12.559
As long as we package you right,

00:01:12.639 --> 00:01:13.959
getting on TV won't be a problem.

00:01:14.599 --> 00:01:16.120
We'll sign the contract in a bit

00:01:16.639 --> 00:01:18.080
From now on, we're family

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:20.080
Just call me Sister Amy

00:01:27.839 --> 00:01:28.400
Sister Amy

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:31.199
This is

00:01:32.160 --> 00:01:33.199
Her name is Zeng Lili

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:34.760
She's our company's top girl

00:01:35.480 --> 00:01:36.680
Never mind her foot.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.800
She uses it to stir up hype

00:01:39.199 --> 00:01:41.480
She's insanely popular online

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:42.959
You don't know?

00:01:43.239 --> 00:01:45.160
These days, some rich photographers

00:01:45.160 --> 00:01:46.919
just love shooting this "broken beauty" stuff

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:51.279
Let's go

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:04.199
Princess

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:06.319
Why not use your cash superpowers?

00:02:06.519 --> 00:02:07.639
If you don't buy votes,

00:02:07.760 --> 00:02:09.759
you'll be out in round one

00:02:10.039 --> 00:02:11.320
What's the point of buying votes?

00:02:11.880 --> 00:02:13.199
I'm going to win with real ability

00:02:14.240 --> 00:02:15.320
Ability?

00:02:15.639 --> 00:02:16.440
Here,

00:02:16.440 --> 00:02:18.039
whoever's sugar daddy has clout

00:02:18.039 --> 00:02:19.080
is the one with "ability"

00:02:29.160 --> 00:02:29.839
Haozi

00:02:30.199 --> 00:02:31.199
Get the vote count up

00:02:31.679 --> 00:02:32.199
Got it

00:02:42.199 --> 00:02:43.160
Damn

00:02:43.160 --> 00:02:44.759
Voting texts are one yuan each

00:02:44.839 --> 00:02:45.960
How much is that gonna cost?

00:02:47.199 --> 00:02:47.720
Sis

00:02:48.039 --> 00:02:49.080
Who the hell are you?

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:50.000
Your votes just shot right past

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.279
our company's top girl's.

00:02:52.440 --> 00:02:53.960
How did they jump so much all at once?

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:57.479
First place!

00:02:57.679 --> 00:02:58.800
She's actually in first place!

00:02:58.800 --> 00:02:59.279
Who is she?

00:02:59.279 --> 00:03:00.360
She's even higher than Lili

00:03:00.440 --> 00:03:01.880
She hit first place that fast?

00:03:03.479 --> 00:03:04.279
Lin Shen

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:07.160
I knew you weren't ordinary

00:03:07.279 --> 00:03:08.119
President Wang said

00:03:08.399 --> 00:03:09.479
he wants to see you in person

00:03:20.119 --> 00:03:21.479
You're the new girl

00:03:22.399 --> 00:03:23.320
Xiao Shen, you're here.

00:03:23.559 --> 00:03:24.320
Come in

00:03:39.160 --> 00:03:41.800
I heard we got a rising star at the company

00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:43.240
Come, come

00:03:43.279 --> 00:03:44.279
Sit, sit, sit

00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:52.199
Not bad

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.600
Not bad

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.240
You're truly beautiful

00:04:02.759 --> 00:04:03.559
But

00:04:04.639 --> 00:04:05.679
your feet

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:08.320
are even more beautiful

00:04:09.320 --> 00:04:10.279
Thank you, President Wang

00:04:10.839 --> 00:04:11.839
With your recognition,

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.000
in the competition,

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:14.279
I'll definitely achieve great results

00:04:15.679 --> 00:04:17.040
Do your best, okay

00:04:26.640 --> 00:04:27.320
I need to take a call

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:28.399
You rest for a bit

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:42.519
As long as you let my son go,

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:43.920
we can talk about anything

00:05:09.839 --> 00:05:11.359
Rookies are always like this

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:13.519
They don't know their place

00:05:14.519 --> 00:05:16.079
The higher they're lifted up,

00:05:16.200 --> 00:05:17.559
the harder they crash

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:18.959
I'm telling you,

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:20.720
you should just go home while you can

00:05:21.200 --> 00:05:22.000
Lili

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:24.160
You don't have to see me as competition

00:05:24.799 --> 00:05:26.119
I won't be in this business for long

00:05:27.320 --> 00:05:29.239
I'm only here because of my jerk ex,

00:05:29.239 --> 00:05:31.079
so I wanted to see for myself

00:05:31.079 --> 00:05:33.119
what this whole talent show thing really is

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:35.480
All this over that?

00:05:37.559 --> 00:05:38.359
Men,

00:05:38.679 --> 00:05:39.600
aren't they all the same?

00:05:39.839 --> 00:05:41.399
It's not like you can't find a better one

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:44.239
You have no idea.

00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:45.440
In our line of work,

00:05:45.839 --> 00:05:47.559
as long as you have a bit of money,

00:05:47.559 --> 00:05:49.079
you won't find any good people around you

00:05:49.640 --> 00:05:50.920
My ex was just like that

00:05:51.559 --> 00:05:53.920
Just like our boss's son

00:05:54.920 --> 00:05:56.079
Idling around all day doing nothing

00:06:03.679 --> 00:06:04.720
Let me tell you something juicy

00:06:05.839 --> 00:06:07.079
The boss's son

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:08.959
got kidnapped

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:11.040
Did you know?

00:06:11.200 --> 00:06:12.399
Even a newbie like me knows,

00:06:12.440 --> 00:06:13.359
so you must know too

00:06:15.359 --> 00:06:17.320
No wonder I haven't seen Li Hu lately

00:06:18.519 --> 00:06:19.679
I'm telling you,

00:06:19.679 --> 00:06:20.920
this business is shady.

00:06:21.200 --> 00:06:22.559
Get out while you still can.

00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:24.200
Lili

00:06:24.839 --> 00:06:25.720
Who is Li Hu?

00:06:26.959 --> 00:06:27.679
Him?

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:30.559
He used to be Wang Dahai's driver

00:06:31.239 --> 00:06:33.200
He hung out with that rich kid every day

00:06:33.480 --> 00:06:34.519
Drinking, whoring, gambling

00:06:34.519 --> 00:06:35.359
He got into everything

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:42.359
Li Hu

00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:43.399
Thirty-five years old

00:06:43.760 --> 00:06:45.359
He and Wang Dongdong are birds of a feather

00:06:45.679 --> 00:06:46.480
Addicted to gambling

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:48.440
But when Wang Dongdong loses,

00:06:48.600 --> 00:06:49.839
his dad covers for him

00:06:50.119 --> 00:06:51.200
Li Hu is the one who's screwed

00:06:51.519 --> 00:06:52.559
He owes a mountain of debt

00:06:52.559 --> 00:06:53.640
His wife even divorced him

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:55.640
Captain

00:06:56.399 --> 00:06:57.559
Through canvassing, we found out

00:06:57.559 --> 00:06:58.799
Wang Dongdong last showed up

00:06:58.799 --> 00:07:00.040
near an old residential complex

00:07:02.119 --> 00:07:03.959
An old residential complex?

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.559
He's a rich kid

00:07:05.559 --> 00:07:06.559
What would he be doing there?

00:07:08.600 --> 00:07:09.399
Maybe gambling

00:07:10.519 --> 00:07:12.279
Are there any underground casinos around there?

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:13.440
Shi Lei

00:07:13.880 --> 00:07:14.799
Prepare the paperwork

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:16.200
Go ask the Public Security Brigade

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:17.640
See if there are any gambling dens nearby

00:07:30.119 --> 00:07:31.600
Public Security reported to command

00:07:31.799 --> 00:07:33.480
that the case may involve organized crime

00:07:34.279 --> 00:07:35.519
The department leadership instructed us

00:07:35.519 --> 00:07:36.839
to work the case jointly with them.

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:15.559
Police! Don't move!

00:08:16.839 --> 00:08:17.440
Where are you standing?

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:18.519
Don't move. Squat down.

00:08:18.799 --> 00:08:20.279
Squat down. Don't move.

00:08:20.880 --> 00:08:21.760
Behave yourself.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:24.440
Don't move.

00:08:24.799 --> 00:08:25.880
Don't move, hear me?

00:08:27.799 --> 00:08:29.559
Don't move. Behave yourself!

00:08:33.359 --> 00:08:33.960
Talk.

00:08:34.280 --> 00:08:35.640
Has Wang Dongdong been here lately?

00:08:36.559 --> 00:08:37.679
Wang Dongdong?

00:08:38.599 --> 00:08:40.239
He hasn't come for days.

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:42.880
He's got a serious addiction.

00:08:42.880 --> 00:08:43.799
He owes us a lot of money.

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:45.559
We haven't found him yet.

00:08:45.599 --> 00:08:46.640
I-I know.

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:47.479
I know.

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:50.159
If I tell you...

00:08:50.479 --> 00:08:52.520
Can you go easy on me?

00:08:52.520 --> 00:08:53.880
If you don't talk now,

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:55.239
then you're in danger right now.

00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:56.080
No, no...

00:08:56.239 --> 00:08:57.520
I'll talk, I'll talk!

00:08:57.960 --> 00:08:59.039
Well...

00:08:59.200 --> 00:09:01.479
The last time Wang Dongdong came,

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:03.960
he came with Li Hu.

00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:06.080
Where does Li Hu usually go?

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:07.599
I know, I know, I know!

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:08.880
Madam Officer...

00:09:09.239 --> 00:09:10.159
When the time comes, could you...

00:09:10.159 --> 00:09:11.400
put in a good word for me?

00:09:11.400 --> 00:09:13.440
Just let me off this once.

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:14.799
How many people here

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:16.000
have had their families ruined by you?

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:17.280
Did you ever let them off?

00:09:17.479 --> 00:09:19.239
And you still dare bargain with us?

00:09:19.359 --> 00:09:21.080
I'll talk! I'll talk! I'll talk!

00:09:21.159 --> 00:09:22.440
That Li Hu...

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:24.719
used to be Wang Dongdong's dad's driver.

00:09:24.960 --> 00:09:26.479
They... they often hung out at...

00:09:28.719 --> 00:09:29.960
Who is it? Who is it?

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:30.520
Don't move!

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:32.359
Don't shoot! Don't shoot! Don't shoot!

00:09:32.400 --> 00:09:33.080
Are you Li Hu?

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:35.640
I'm Li Hu, I'm Li Hu, Li Hu!

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:36.159
Take him away.

00:09:36.239 --> 00:09:36.880
Take him away.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:41.520
Ow, ow, ow!

00:09:41.520 --> 00:09:42.039
Don't move.

00:09:46.599 --> 00:09:47.400
Move.

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:58.559
I...

00:09:58.960 --> 00:10:00.479
I'm gonna use the restroom first.

00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:04.280
No cold drinks before your period.

00:10:04.719 --> 00:10:05.840
No wonder it hurts like hell.

00:10:07.479 --> 00:10:08.679
I was just frustrated.

00:10:08.679 --> 00:10:10.440
Drank something cold to cool off.

00:10:11.159 --> 00:10:13.159
Besides, I've got you, don't I?

00:10:13.159 --> 00:10:14.719
Bringing me the warmth of a spring breeze,

00:10:14.719 --> 00:10:15.919
staying by my side to take care of me.

00:10:15.919 --> 00:10:17.479
Cut the crap.

00:10:17.919 --> 00:10:19.880
Next time it hurts, take a painkiller.

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:21.080
Don't tough it out.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.679
I don't want my mission report to say

00:10:23.679 --> 00:10:25.159
that you got hurt because of cramps.

00:10:25.520 --> 00:10:27.479
If you care about me, just say so.

00:10:27.479 --> 00:10:28.359
Still acting tough.

00:10:29.200 --> 00:10:30.239
Saying one thing, meaning another.

00:10:30.520 --> 00:10:31.239
Go on, hurry up.

00:10:31.239 --> 00:10:32.320
This way.

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:37.880
Officers...

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:40.239
I already told you.

00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:40.840
This was all...

00:10:43.239 --> 00:10:45.200
planned by Wang Dongdong.

00:10:45.359 --> 00:10:46.799
I was just the hired help.

00:10:49.080 --> 00:10:50.200
He told me

00:10:50.479 --> 00:10:52.080
his dad is stingy.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:53.640
Each time, he'd only give him

00:10:53.640 --> 00:10:54.799
ten or twenty thousand yuan.

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:56.880
Put it another way,

00:10:57.239 --> 00:10:57.880
that ten or twenty thousand

00:10:57.880 --> 00:11:00.000
isn't even enough for one bet, right?

00:11:00.919 --> 00:11:03.320
Loan sharks were after me. I had no choice.

00:11:03.599 --> 00:11:04.400
So...

00:11:04.400 --> 00:11:05.239
I figured

00:11:05.679 --> 00:11:06.479
we'd scam his dad,

00:11:06.599 --> 00:11:07.719
stage a fake kidnapping.

00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:09.280
He told me

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:11.239
we could get one million.

00:11:13.799 --> 00:11:14.960
What's with the ear?

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:17.520
He did it.

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:18.559
He said

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:19.880
it couldn't look too fake.

00:11:20.239 --> 00:11:21.479
So I thought

00:11:21.479 --> 00:11:23.159
if you aren't willing to risk the kid,

00:11:23.239 --> 00:11:24.799
you won't catch the wolf, right?

00:11:24.919 --> 00:11:25.679
We had to make it real.

00:11:25.679 --> 00:11:27.400
What if he actually won big?

00:11:29.520 --> 00:11:30.919
You really are a hard-core gambler.

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:35.000
So why cut off an ear?

00:11:35.400 --> 00:11:36.400
Your ear...

00:11:36.479 --> 00:11:38.080
you willingly let him cut it off?

00:11:38.760 --> 00:11:40.080
The guy is sick in the head.

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:41.840
What normal person

00:11:41.840 --> 00:11:43.320
watches "Black Cat Detective" every day?

00:11:43.799 --> 00:11:44.840
That mouse in the show

00:11:45.239 --> 00:11:46.400
actually gave him the idea.

00:11:51.880 --> 00:11:53.200
Who's talking about me?

00:11:57.280 --> 00:11:58.119
At the time,

00:11:58.760 --> 00:11:59.919
he told me

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:02.320
as long as the money came through,

00:12:02.840 --> 00:12:04.559
we'd be set for the rest of our lives.

00:12:04.799 --> 00:12:05.799
And as for my ear,

00:12:05.799 --> 00:12:07.200
it wouldn't have been cut for nothing.

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:10.200
Now look at this.

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:12.119
The money's gone,

00:12:12.880 --> 00:12:14.320
and I'm missing an ear.

00:12:16.440 --> 00:12:18.239
What am I gonna do with my life now?

00:12:21.359 --> 00:12:22.640
Where is Wang Dongdong now?

00:12:23.359 --> 00:12:24.159
Where's he hiding?

00:12:24.640 --> 00:12:25.960
I know that.

00:12:26.119 --> 00:12:27.479
Down in the south of the city,

00:12:27.479 --> 00:12:28.559
at that old factory.

00:12:28.760 --> 00:12:29.880
He even complained about me.

00:12:29.960 --> 00:12:30.679
Saying that...

00:12:30.679 --> 00:12:32.080
my ear smelled like blood.

00:12:32.239 --> 00:12:33.840
He said when the real deal goes down,

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:34.840
he'll call me over.

00:12:36.400 --> 00:12:37.840
Officers...

00:12:38.239 --> 00:12:39.479
It was all planned by him.

00:12:40.599 --> 00:12:42.359
I'm half a victim too, right?

00:12:48.359 --> 00:12:49.080
Mr. Wang.

00:12:49.559 --> 00:12:51.400
That's basically the situation.

00:12:53.119 --> 00:12:53.840
Ungrateful brat!

00:12:53.840 --> 00:12:55.359
He's an ungrateful brat.

00:12:55.559 --> 00:12:57.320
How could I have a son like this?

00:12:58.000 --> 00:12:58.840
He actually...

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:00.280
He actually did it to trick me...

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:03.440
Just for money...

00:13:03.960 --> 00:13:06.119
He teamed up with someone to scam me.

00:13:06.200 --> 00:13:07.320
To scam me!

00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:08.479
My own son...

00:13:08.479 --> 00:13:09.320
Officer...

00:13:09.479 --> 00:13:10.599
I'm not filing a report anymore.

00:13:10.599 --> 00:13:11.119
Withdraw the case.

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:11.880
Withdraw it!

00:13:12.039 --> 00:13:12.559
I...

00:13:13.159 --> 00:13:14.599
I'll let him fend for himself.

00:13:14.599 --> 00:13:15.119
Please don't get worked up.

00:13:15.159 --> 00:13:16.000
This is the police station.

00:13:16.039 --> 00:13:16.599
Please mind yourself.

00:13:16.760 --> 00:13:17.200
Mind yourself.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:17.760
Mr. Wang.

00:13:18.440 --> 00:13:19.039
Mr. Wang!

00:13:19.719 --> 00:13:21.039
You need to calm down.

00:13:21.119 --> 00:13:22.919
We still need to see him in person.

00:13:24.679 --> 00:13:25.559
Yes, yes, yes.

00:13:26.559 --> 00:13:27.400
Answer the phone.

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:29.919
Hello?

00:13:31.599 --> 00:13:32.440
He's gone missing.